		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Using_&quot;hao&quot;_to_mean_&quot;easy&quot;" title="Using &quot;hao&quot; to mean &quot;easy&quot;">Using "hao" to mean "easy"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">A2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;hard_to_avoid&quot;_with_&quot;nanmian&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;hard to avoid&quot; with &quot;nanmian&quot;">Expressing "hard to avoid" with "nanmian"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_difficulty_with_&quot;hao_(bu)_rongyi&quot;" title="Expressing difficulty with &quot;hao (bu) rongyi&quot;">Expressing difficulty with "hao (bu) rongyi"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
